.TH Balsa 1 "18 Aug 1998" Version 0.4.0
.SH NAME
Balsa - the GNOME email client.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B balsa
[\-h] [\-\-help] [-v] [\-\-version]


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\fIBalsa\fP is a e-mail reader.  This client is part of the GNOME desktop
environment.  It supports local mailboxes, POP3 and IMAP.

